 you like: droppers, mini games. The possiblities are endless!<br></li><li> <strong>Workshop integration</strong><br>Download custom maps made by others, or upload your own custom maps!<br></li><li> <strong>Leaderboards</strong><br>Compete against other players for the best time in a test chamber!</li></ul></h2><br><br><br><strong>Controller Support:</strong><br>The game has full controller support, except for the in-game level editor, which is why it is flagged as Partial Controller Support.",
